<h4>About</h4> <p> This project is a comprehensive digital library management system designed to manage the information of books and authors efficiently. With a user-friendly interface, users can securely create accounts and log in to the system, ensuring a personalized experience tailored to their needs. </p> <h4>Key Features</h4> <ul> <li><strong>User Authentication:</strong> Users can create accounts and log in securely to access the system.</li> <li><strong>Book Management:</strong> Easily add, edit, or delete book records to keep the library's collection up to date.</li> <li><strong>Author Management:</strong> Seamlessly manage author information, including adding new authors and editing existing records.</li> <li><strong>Detailed Views:</strong> Access comprehensive details about each book and author, enhancing user knowledge and research capabilities.</li> <li><strong>Search Functionality:</strong> Quickly search for specific books or authors, making information retrieval efficient.</li> </ul> <h4>Objective</h4> <p> The system aims to provide an efficient, organized, and user-friendly way to manage a library’s collection. By digitizing the library's information, we make it easier for users to maintain and access essential data, ultimately enhancing the overall library experience. </p>